command: from lifesim.stats import StatsCollector; from lifesim.types import StepResult, WorldState, TickMetrics, Position, Agent; ws = WorldState(5, 5, 1, 42, ((Position(0,0), Agent(10, 1, 0)),)); sr = StepResult(world=ws, births=1, deaths=2, movements=3); sc = StatsCollector(); tm = sc.record(sr); assert tm.population == 1 and tm.births == 1 and tm.deaths == 2 and tm.avg_energy == 10.0
